data.description: Motivated seller, Offering $5,000 credit towards buyers closing costs! This 3 BR, 2 BA home is just 3 minutes from downtown DeLand & Stetson University. This concrete block gem offers a carport, mature trees for privacy, and a spacious backyard with a fire pit, two orange trees, and a plantain tree. This quiet street is perfect for a family, college student, or first-time home buyer. The A/C is 2020; The Current sellers have replaced the plumbing under the home from 1971. They also added laundry hookups in the utility room off the kitchen for convenience. The washer and dryer are included!
